hasMenuItem.name: Fall in Love 2024
hasMenuItem.description:
Enjoy all the flavours of fall with this warm, light, yet full of flavour pumpkin pizza. Ingredients are: Bechamel sauce, mozzarella, thinly sliced fresh pumpkin with a hint of pumpkin spice, Provolone cheese imported from Italy, Pancetta, and a dash of Nutmeg.
Warning: Don't fall too much in love as this is a seasonal pizza!

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Explosion of Veggies
hasMenuItem.description:
Bringing the explosion of veggies to another level. No wonder this pizza has been the #1 seller since opening day.
This pizza is full of fresh veggies, low in fat, high in nutrients and now we are offering it to you with 100% plant based cheese.  
San Marzano tomato sauce, vegan cheese, spinach, mushrooms, cherry tomatoes, bell peppers, and red onions.

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Pizzette 8 small slices
hasMenuItem.description: Pizzetta can be served as an hors d'oeuvre, a snack food and as a light meal. It may be served accompanied with wine to complement the dish. It’s also great for kids!

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Pizzette cut into 16 slice pizzas
hasMenuItem.description: Pizzetta can be served as an hors d'oeuvre, a snack food and as a light meal. It may be served accompanied with wine to complement the dish. It’s also great for kids! These small slices are made on our easy digestible dough topped with San Marzano tomato sauce, a dash of salt and extra virgin olive oil... simple yet delicious!

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Queen Margherita
hasMenuItem.description:
This pizza is for everyone. So soft and crispy, full of flavour with only high quality ingredients. Let the cheese melt in your mouth, sit back and enjoy this unique and authentic pizza. This is definitely a must!

San Marzano Tomato Sauce, 100% Plant based mozzarella cheese, Cherry tomatoes, Vegan Burrata, basil leaves, and a drizzle of EVOO

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Santorini
hasMenuItem.description: You don’t have to compromise to enjoy our mediterranean pizza. Enjoy it with tomato sauce, a delicious and unique vegan cheese, kalamata olives, artichoke hearts, bell peppers, red onions, oregano, vegan burrata cheese, and orange zest.

hasMenuItem.name: Vegan Panzerotti
hasMenuItem.description:
This soft and crispy Panzerotti is to die for. Freshly baked on every order and big enough to share. Low in fat and now with 100% plant based Burrata cheese this panzerotti just got even better.
Freshly baked homemade bread, Arugula, cherry tomatoes, vegan burrata, a drizzle of EVOO, a dash of Pink salt and a drizzle of balsamic glaze. 
Feeds 2

review.reviewBody: Always amazing food and staff is beyond incredible! Our Friday routine is to end the week with their delicious pizza and Panna Cotta <3

delicious pizza, Friday nights especially. I've had a couple of issues with some of the orders (missing ingredients, generally), but staff are always friendly, price is fair for the quality and amount.
Have not been dissapoint yet with a pizza from Nat's.
forgot the basil the first time, reordered through customer service for the correct pizza, forgot the basil again.... idek.
Don't order the Caesar.... for $17 you get a handful of wilting lettuce and PACKAGED dressing made by pepper mill!!  Not homemade
